#IMAGINE OPENBOX THEME STRUCTURE
#by ishom jauhari (ishomj@gmail.com)
#Theme name - Imagine Radiance
#
#Goal of IMAGINE THEMING is to produce openbox theme that
#border looks thick, inactive looks behind active window
#remove square impression button & in different colors, how can be?
#button marks is designed based on box concept
#
